text: "Rosalita (Come Out Tonight)" is a 1973 song by Bruce Springsteen. It was taken from his second studio album The Wild, the Innocent & the E Street Shuffle. It was never released as a single in the United States and was released as a single in the Netherlands in 1979. ==References== Category:1973 songs Category:1979 songs Category:Bruce Springsteen songs
